description:
One day, I introduced myself at my new school and when I was about to take my seat, I was suddenly swallowed by a light and lost consciousness.

When I opened my eyes, I found myself in a white and gray space …There’s someone who got down on his knees…?

Apparently, the gods got the capacity wrong and I couldn’t get back to my world. Moreover, I can’t just go to the transference site as I am…?

If I can’t go home. I’ll live free over here!

On Earth, I was oppressed in a lot of ways because of my looks. We don’t get oppressed over here! …Yeah!

Huh? What about the other summoned people? ……… Well, I guess it’s okay!

And then the girl? Let’s live well and free in another world!>
